read sequence coor name "1bni_stripped_in_A.crd" resid 
generate setup A first ACE last CT1

read coor card name "1bni_stripped_in_A.crd"

hbuild sele segid A .and. hydrogen end

ic para
ic build

hbuild sele segid A .and. hydrogen end

ic para
ic build

